{"tid":1592553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[良心市集]今個禮拜入油塘撐左佢地先","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T18:44:29.000Z","uid":83478,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9950206de2c6656b7ae0940590729c6494ef1b08","tid":1592553,"uid":83478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:09:47.000Z","msg":"大家好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想同大家推介一個市集, 市集搞手、場地、擺檔檔主都好黃好值得大家支持！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞手仲將部份收入捐俾星火添，而檔主，更有部份自發性義賣活動，都係捐俾有需要團體！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實良心小店應該包括埋手作小店/檔主, 呢3個幾月影響佢地都好多，以往佢地好多時便靠週末擺市集賺錢，但呢排大家都冇心機行市集，而佢地！！好多都寧願出去發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!! 佢地好多都係全職手作人，點解佢地咁傻仲要cut自己搵錢機會又就算有得擺市集都要捐錢？因為佢地想用自己方式去撐香港撐香港人！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家今個禮拜六或日搵個時間入油塘，用金錢攻撃去懲罰佢地啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地手製既野都好多同運動有關！！絕對買得過support得過架！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHtAyp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHtAyp2.jpg&h=4a91a23b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nnomad nomad x TTN 市集 - 慣性定律<br />\n活動專頁：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2363254493949318/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2363254493949318%2F&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUr7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=e01b1f22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/2363254493949318/</a><br />\n活動詳情-<br />\n日期：28-29/9/2019<br />\n時間：14:00-20:00<br />\n地點：This Town Needs (TTN)<br />\n地址：油塘崇信街6號Ocean One一樓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JVYs8YF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJVYs8YF.jpg&h=e36adbfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家見唔見倒樹上有喺咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mW6E5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9mW6E5c.jpg&h=d38c69f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NVh2dqd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVh2dqd.png&h=3e43c3ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mamKrLe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmamKrLe.jpg&h=ac79b055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢位檔主有好多相關印仔俾大家任吸，連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連豬都有<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MShaniV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMShaniV.png&h=7983caa0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyqZZ5B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyqZZ5B.jpg&h=63abc586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢2檔傻架 賺既都全數捐俾星火！！佢地d料都唔平架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64kWhSC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64kWhSC.jpg&h=e7d2c0fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3bjspxE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3bjspxE.jpg&h=954c22e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jbdg2jk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJbdg2jk.jpg&h=d2eec7b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有唔同好值得買既反送中為題既創作！！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家支持<img src=\"/